    • Method Detail

      • getOtherAtom

        Atom getOtherAtom(Atom a)
        Get the other Atom in this bond that is not the passed in Atom. If the passed in Atom is "atom 1" then this will return "atom 2" and vice versa.
        Parameters:
        a - the Atom in the bond NOT to return; can not be null.
        Returns:
        the other Atom; will not be null.
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if a is null.
